    "or_image_text_G7Km3L": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_dxU6AF": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "RECYCLED 925 STERLING SILVER //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_qnxRzb": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All Phoria pieces are made using 100% recycled and certified solid 925 sterling silver, which is 92.5% pure silver mixed with alloys (a combination of other metals). This is a recognized standard for high-quality silver as pure silver is too soft to be used in jewellery for everyday wear as it is susceptible to bending, scratching, and other forms of damage. The remaining 7.5% of alloys makes the silver a highly durable material.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_qKCjLM": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Recycled 925 sterling silver is exactly the same in quality as non-recycled 925 sterling silver, the difference is in the source of the silver used, not the quality of the material itself as it is only produced by reusing existing 925 sterling silver materials. This is a more sustainable and eco-friendly option as it reduces the need for new mining therefore reduces CO2 emissions.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_R9yBrz": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our pieces are hallmarked and lasered with a 925 mark for authenticity, which means you can trust that every item is of the 925 quality.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_dxU6AF",
        "richtext_qnxRzb",
        "richtext_qKCjLM",
        "richtext_R9yBrz"
      ],
      "custom_css": [
        ".or-redesignable-feature {margin-top: -10.5vw; pointer-events: none;}",
        "@media screen and (max-width: 1020px) {.or-redesignable-feature {margin-top: 0; }}"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "right",
        "text_alignment": "right",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/2-2023-05-17-sm-phoria-shot-03-323-v1-silver-5x4-300dpi-1.jpg",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000"
