    "or_image_text_NVVtTy": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_nqV9NP": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Recycled 18CT Gold Vermeil //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_gKjii8": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our yellow gold plated pieces are made from 18 ct Gold Vermeil (pronounced ‘ver-may’). This means that their base metal is 925 sterling silver and are plated in 18 carat Yellow Gold. Our plating is 2.5 microns thick which is 5x thicker than the average gold plating and is plated with a process known as ‘electrolysis’ making it very durable.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_YYYq78": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We use the highest percentage of gold alloy that is durable for everyday wear, which is 18 carats. 20 and 24 carat gold are relatively soft and are more prone to show signs of wear.<br/>Gold Vermeil allows us to create pieces that combine fashion and fine jewellery at an affordable price point. If you want the look and feel of high-quality gold without the high price tag this is for you!</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_gcfUDe": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our pieces are hallmarked and lasered with a 925 mark for authenticity, which means you can trust that every piece has a 925 quality base.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_nqV9NP",
        "richtext_gKjii8",
        "richtext_YYYq78",
        "richtext_gcfUDe"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "left",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/4-2023-05-17-sm-phoria-shot-05-329-final-5x4-300dpi.jpg",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000"
      }
    },
    "or_image_text_LxBLqn": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_JMYkgD": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Rhodium Plating //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_F8hMhG": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our two-toned rings and earrings are rhodium plated on their silver side. This provides an extremely tough and protective layer against tarnishing for durability as sterling silver is a relatively soft metal and it can be prone to scratching over time. Silver also naturally tarnishes when it comes into contact with oxygen and sulfur compounds in the air. The rhodium plating acts as a barrier, preventing the silver from interacting with these compounds and reducing tarnish. This means that rhodium-plated silver jewelry requires less frequent cleaning and maintenance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_inQAWg": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Rhodium is also hypoallergenic, which means it is less likely to cause allergic reactions compared to some other metals so is great for people with sensitive skin.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_JMYkgD",
        "richtext_F8hMhG",
        "richtext_inQAWg"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "right",
        "text_alignment": "right",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/2023_05_17_SM_PHORIA_SHOT_06_112_FINAL_1X1_300DPI.webp",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000"
      }
    },
    "or_image_text_wxDgm7": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_MhCVJ9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Semi Precious White Topaz Gemstones //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_j8RnrW": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We use natural white topaz gemstones as they are considered the semi-precious alternative to a diamond in the jewellery world. We want to make sure that our jewellery is affordable and white topaz enables us to have a natural gemstone with a diamond-like appearance without the high price tag.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_AYjnLG": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We make sure that we source well-cut white topaz so that they exhibit excellent brilliance, clarity and sparkle.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_LiV3Li": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our gemstones are natural and sourced from all over the world which means that every stone is unique. This may mean that some stones might look different to others but this just makes each one of a kind!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_MhCVJ9",
        "richtext_j8RnrW",
        "richtext_AYjnLG",
        "richtext_LiV3Li"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
