    "or_image_text_wVVkKD": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_bKBKYM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Semi-Precious Chrome Diopside Gemstones //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_YiPgKw": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We use natural chrome diopside gemstones as they are considered the semi-precious alternative to an emerald in the jewellery world. We want to make sure that our jewellery is affordable and chrome diopside enables us to have a natural gemstone with an emerald-like appearance without the high price tag.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_3t39Vn": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We make sure that we source well-cut chrome diopside so that they exhibit excellent brilliance, clarity and sparkle. The stones may appear lighter than a deep emerald green and more like a peridot as they are all small in size (this can naturally happen when they are smaller as they allow more light to pass through them). We love this green shade though as it’s so vibrant!</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_T8jgfF": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All of our gemstones are natural and sourced from all over the world which means that every stone is unique. This may mean that some stones might look different to others but this just makes each one of a kind!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_bKBKYM",
        "richtext_YiPgKw",
        "richtext_3t39Vn",
        "richtext_T8jgfF"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "right",
