    "or_image_text_6LK6Q6": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_yPFmCT": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hallmarking //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_bpqE8i": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Each and every piece of Phoria Jewellery has been hallmarked by the Goldsmiths Company Assay Office in London. This means that every piece is officially marked and certified to verify their composition and quality so you can trust that every item you buy from us is made from 925 Sterling Silver.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_rztzBL": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>In the UK it is illegal to sell or describe any item as gold or silver unless it is hallmarked. To learn more about these marks and what they mean please view this<a href=\"https://www.assayofficelondon.co.uk/media/2635/e3087_london-dealer-notice-updates-sep-19-single-sided.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Dealers Notice\">Dealers Notice</a>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_Yb7gB8": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Phoria Jewellery is hallmarked by laser engraving and is made fairly small in size (so might not be visible straight away) so that it is kept discreet and doesn’t take over the piece.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_yPFmCT",
        "richtext_bpqE8i",
        "richtext_rztzBL",
        "richtext_Yb7gB8"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "right",
        "text_alignment": "right",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/hallmarking.webp",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000"
      }
    },
    "or_image_text_DGccC3": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_eVTtcm": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Our storage packaging + care //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_UqUnLc": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All Phoria jewellery comes in a complimentary air-tight jewellery box to keep your piece in when it’s not being worn. Simply remove the black insert (if you didn’t order a chain) in your green box by lifting up the tab to reveal the tray.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_x7wQdQ": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Keeping your piece in an air-tight box helps to prevent oxidation which happens naturally when certain metals are in contact with air, particularly with silver. When jewellery oxidises it develops tarnish which can make your jewellery appear dull or discoloured. Keeping your piece in an air-tight box helps to create a barrier between the air and therefore helps to prevent tarnish. It will also help keep away dust and dirt to keep it’s cleanliness and appearance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_QyRwKf": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If your jewellery is stored for long periods of time, we recommend cleaning it occasionally to keep the process at bay. Wearing your jewellery often helps to slow down the oxidation process!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_eVTtcm",
        "richtext_UqUnLc",
        "richtext_x7wQdQ",
        "richtext_QyRwKf"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "left",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Packaging-boxes-2.jpg",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000"
      }
    },
    "or_image_text_Yixzf4": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_MkzfPe": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Care + Cleaning Sterling Silver Jewellery //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_kbdpCB": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>All Phoria jewellery comes with a care card and polishing cloth with details of how to care for your piece. It’s good practice to clean your jewellery regularly using the cloth provided.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_rwKTD9": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We advise you to avoid contact with chemicals, so please remove your jewellery when using cleaning products, applying lotions like fake tan, cosmetics, perfumes or hairsprays, as these can damage the silver.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_zQPJV9": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We also advise you to remove your jewellery before showering to reduce how exposed to moisture they are. Wait until any products are dry on your skin before putting your jewellery back on.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_PnEXUa": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To clean your jewellery or to restore its shine, use the polishing cloth provided to you to gently wipe any fingerprints, dirt and oils. You can also use any commercial silver polish. Follow the product’s instructions and rub the cloth or polish onto the jewellery in gentle, circular motions. Be careful not to over-polish, as excessive polishing can wear away the silver. Avoid abrasive materials like paper towels, as they can scratch the silver.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_YkEVYq": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If your jewellery needs a more thorough cleaning, create a mixture of mild dish soap and warm water. Dip a soft cloth or a soft-bristle toothbrush in the soapy water, and gently scrub the silver. Rinse thoroughly with clean water and make sure to pat dry with a clean cloth.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_hJxrmP": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If your piece has naturally tarnished over time (which happens particularly to silver) – the best way to prevent this is to wear your jewellery regularly! The natural oils in your skin can help protect and maintain silver’s luster.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_MkzfPe",
        "richtext_kbdpCB",
        "richtext_rwKTD9",
        "richtext_zQPJV9",
        "richtext_PnEXUa",
        "richtext_YkEVYq",
        "richtext_hJxrmP"
      ],
